citation: Land Use Planning and Approvals Amendment (Validation) Act 2009 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Land Use Planning and Approvals Amendment (Validation) Act 2009 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Land Use Planning and Approvals Amendment (Validation) Act 2009 has been repealed by Schedule 1 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
